latestPosts.caption:
Celebrating love, style, and everything elegant on our anniversary!
Wearing this ready-to-wear drape saree by @house_of_hoonar made me feel nothing less than a diva!
The high-neck organza blouse, fully hand-embroidered with pearls and zari, was pure art—unlined at the back, giving it that subtle and sexy allure.

The lightest green shade of the outfit was a breath of fresh elegance.
The pre-pleated skirt featured a drape-style pallu gracefully set on the shoulder with a statement brooch—perfectly pinned to stay put and slay! The pearl-detailed waistband added a regal touch that made the entire ensemble stand out.

Styled it with long pearl earrings, a green jadau kada, a pearl bracelet, and two stunning cocktail rings—one in pearl, one in emerald green—from the fabulous @bharti_jewellers  Every piece added a sparkle of royalty.

Makeup & hair by my favourite @rubeezmakeover , who always knows how to bring out the best in me.
From head to toe, I felt confident, classy, and completely in love—with the look and the moment!

The location is my favorite and one of the best rooftop lounge @aerosky_bar_and_kitchen
